  "2215910": {
    "name": "MetaBall - Multiplayer Basketball",
    "steam_appid": 2215910,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/85005c630497458a73e7bbb438dd9c6d.poster.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/85005c630497458a73e7bbb438dd9c6d.webm?t=1755508426\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/85005c630497458a73e7bbb438dd9c6d.mp4?t=1755508426\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/10acac943ba2b55d935c01d6d0d52e5e.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Metaball 是一款支持跨平台的免费在线多人体育游戏，结合了快速移动、刺激的 PvP 比赛和先进的团队合作玩法。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你扮演一名 Rider，努力通过与队友在无情的 Metaball 联赛中获胜，为自己的名字带来名声和财富，同时收集 Metanium 和 MVP 积分。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/f2a10dad3d619e80fbe04be2f0996d25.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/7b52451581c9b84c07e5ad123016c108.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>跳上你的滑板，利用链子抓住球，并运用其摆动的力量执行各种动作。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>扣篮、投篮、封堵和抢球，同时使用氮气提升你的速度或进行双跳或三跳！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在不同的技能树中使用你的技能点，来定制你的游戏风格！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/66442ca7307026ae7032d5af80b4d3ce.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/ded1854d53bdfbb92e2296382fc30a6b.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与其他 Riders 竞争，参与多种 PvP 游戏模式，包括 2v2 和 3v3 快速比赛，或者在学院、冠军之路、自由玩法或自定义比赛模式中磨练你的技能！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/1b1c2b8f97d01cd2b1f5e0ba58ce22ca.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/cb865221458a43020bec45d697299587.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>每场比赛结束后，你将根据结果获得 MVP 积分。所以一定要确保获胜，成为最佳 Rider 以获得额外奖励！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你拥有的 MVP 积分越多，解锁的奖励就越多！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/a8c3066c9567284ee36b64f9b4b5c314.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=104 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2215910/extras/2917179077d8832b7a42a95c440db1a6.avif?t=1755508426\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>利用你辛苦赚来的 Metanium 和 MVP 积分，在 Metapass 中进步，尝试收集你喜欢的装备和物品，在游戏中使用！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>展示的物品可能需要在游戏内商店单独购买，并且受限于库存情况。包含游戏内购买。</i></p>",
